# Routes: chatCompletions

[src/routes/chatCompletions.js](mdc:src/routes/chatCompletions.js) defines the Express router for the `/v1/chat/completions` endpoint:

- Forwards POST requests to the `forwardChatCompletionRequest` controller in [src/controllers/chatCompletions.js](mdc:src/controllers/chatCompletions.js).
- Exported as `chatCompletionsRouter` and used in [src/index.js](mdc:src/index.js) to mount the route.
